IMPORTANT — Before this works, do 2 things:

1. Install pptxgenjs:
   npm install pptxgenjs

2. Add VITE_GROQ_API_KEY to your .env file and Vercel environment variables:
   VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here
   Get it from: https://console.groq.com/keys

3. Run the SQL migration:
   supabase/migrations/002_ppt_versions.sql
   in Supabase SQL Editor
